## Execution Flow

### Before Fixes

```
User Input
    ↓
CLI/Admin/Theme Code
    ↓
Auto-complete (if applicable)
    ↓
No Validation ❌
    ↓
Database Operation
    ↓
Invalid IDs Accepted ❌
```

### After Fixes

```
User Input
    ↓
CLI/Admin/Theme Code
    ↓
Auto-complete (if applicable)
    ↓
Validation Check ✅
    ├─ Valid → Continue
    └─ Invalid → Throw Error
    ↓
Database Operation
    ↓
Only Valid IDs Accepted ✅
```

